column5: Well here I am sitting infront of the puter mad at TSN trying to find the race on line as they think womens soft ball is more inportant then the race I would like to see the number on who is taking time out on sunday to watch it over the race hope the game is over soon. Sorry I am a little mad today I went to go fishing but there were just a few two manny 2' waves at 6am so I turned back and will get out another day
